---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MGEO | Matías Georgetta - Excelencia Legal y Gestión Deportiva">
  
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-dark via-transparent to-brand-dark"></div>
    
    <div class="absolute -top-[10%] -left-[10%] w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-[10%] -right-[10%] w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-brand-primary/15 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl relative z-10 text-center px-6">
      <div class="mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-6 py-2 backdrop-blur-md">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-primary"></span>
        <span class="text-gray-300 font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold">Arquitectura de Resultados</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[11rem] font-heading font-bold leading-none mb-10 tracking-tighter text-white">
        MGEO<span class="text-brand-primary">.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-heading italic font-light text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight mb-12">
        El nexo estratégico entre el <span class="text-white">derecho corporativo</span> y el <span class="text-white">alto rendimiento</span> deportivo.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 pt-6">
        <a href="#unidades" class="group flex items-center gap-4 text-white font-body font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all">
          Explorar Unidades
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-brand-primary group-hover:border-brand-primary transition-all duration-500">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" /></svg>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-white px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-32">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm relative z-10 shadow-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-[1.5s] ease-out">
              <img src="/matias-geo.png" alt="Matías Georgetta" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-brand-light -z-0 opacity-50"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-full h-full border border-brand-dark/5 -z-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:pl-12">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="w-10 h-px bg-brand-primary"></div>
            <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[10px]">Liderazgo Estratégico</span>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-10 tracking-tighter leading-[0.95]">
            Matías Georgetta<br/>
            <span class="text-gray-300 font-light italic">Fundador & Director.</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-600 font-light text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            <!-- <p class="font-heading italic text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-dark leading-snug">
              "El derecho y el alto rendimiento exigen lo mismo: estrategia, precisión y resultados."
            </p> -->
            
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              MGEO nace para brindar una estructura legal que comprenda tanto la norma como el negocio. Fusionamos la rigurosidad de nuestro <span class="text-brand-dark font-medium">Estudio Jurídico</span> con la visión global de nuestra <span class="text-brand-dark font-medium">Agencia Deportiva</span>, blindando el futuro de nuestros clientes en cada escenario.
            </p>
            
            <div class="pt-10 border-t border-gray-100 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-10">
              <div class="flex-1">
                <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-primary font-bold mb-2">Visión Corporativa</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Protección de activos y resolución estratégica de conflictos complejos.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-gray-100"></div>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-primary font-bold mb-2">Proyección Deportiva</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Gestión de carrera bajo los más altos estándares competitivos.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="unidades" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-6xl h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
        <span class="text-brand-primary font-body font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 block">Elige tu camino</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Unidades Operativas</h2>
        <div class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-brand-primary mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-10">
        
        <a href="/estudio" class="group relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-12 overflow-hidden border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-white/5 transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-brand-primary/5">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark z-0 opacity-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829545856-d10d557cf95f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center mix-blend-luminosity opacity-20"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 mb-6 transition-all duration-500 transform group-hover:-translate-y-2 drop-shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(120,22,22,0.4)]">
              <img src="/logo-abogados.png" alt="MGEO Abogados" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6 group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">Estudio Jurídico</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-xs mx-auto mb-8 font-light opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
              Especialistas en ART, Accidentes de Tránsito, Sucesiones y Derecho Corporativo.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-white font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] border-b border-brand-primary pb-2 group-hover:gap-6 transition-all">
              Ingresar <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/sports" class="group relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-12 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-700 hover:bg-brand-primary/5">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark z-0 opacity-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574629810360-7efbbe195018?q=80&w=2036&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center mix-blend-luminosity opacity-20"></div>

          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 mb-6 transition-all duration-500 transform group-hover:-translate-y-2 drop-shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_15px_30px_rgba(120,22,22,0.4)]">
              <img src="/logo-sports.png" alt="MGEO Sports" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6 group-hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">MGEO Sports</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-xs mx-auto mb-8 font-light opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
              Representación estratégica, intermediación y scouting de futbolistas profesionales.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-white font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] border-b border-brand-primary pb-2 group-hover:gap-6 transition-all">
              Ingresar <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" /></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>